      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:6:3:11:16",
      "text": [
        " فِي مُكَاتَبَةٍ يَطَؤُهَا مَوْلَاهَا فَتَحْمِلُ قَالَ يَرُدُّ عَلَيْهَا مَهْرَ مِثْلِهَا وَ تَسْعَى فِي قِيمَتِهَا فَإِنْ عَجَزَتْ فَهِيَ مِنْ أُمَّهَاتِ الْأَوْلَادِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from hi sfather, from Al Nowfaly, from Al Sakuny, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> that Amir Al-Momineen<sup>asws</sup> having said regarding a contracted slave girl, her master copulated with her. He<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘A similar dower would be returned to her, and she would work regarding her price. So if she was frustrated (from paying), so she is from the mothers of the children’."
        ]
      }
    },
